classDiagram
    %% Entities
    class User {
        +userID : String
        +name : String
        +email : String
        +program : String
        +careerGoal : String
        +coursesTaken : List<Course>
    }

    class Course {
        +courseID : String
        +courseName : String
        +category : String
        +difficultyLevel : String
        +workloadLevel : String
        +isPrerequisite : Boolean
        +isActive : Boolean
        +courseDescription : String
        +credit : int
        +department : String
        +prerequisite : List<Course>
    }

    class CoursePlan {
        +planID : String
        +courseList : List<Course>
        +semester : String
        +totalCourses : int
        +graduationGoal : String
        +courseThisSemester : int
        +status : String
    }

    class ChatHistory {
        +sessionID : String
        +userID : String
        +conversationData : JSON
        +timestamp : Date
    }

    %% Relationships between Entities
    User "1" --> "many" CoursePlan : owns
    CoursePlan "many" --> "many" Course : includes
    User "1" --> "many" ChatHistory : has
    Course "many" --> "many" Course : prerequisites

    %% Control classes
    class CourseController {
        +retrieveCourses(User)
        +filterCourses()
        +recommendCourses(User)
    }

    class CoursePlanController {
        +createCoursePlan(User)
        +saveCoursePlan(CoursePlan)
        +modifyCoursePlan(CoursePlan)
        +finalizeCoursePlan(CoursePlan)
    }

    class ChatController {
        +manageConversationFlow()
        +cacheChatHistory(ChatHistory)
        +downloadChatHistory(User)
    }

    class UserController {
        +loginUser(User)
        +manageSession()
        +updateCareerGoal(User)
    }

    %% Boundary classes
    class ChatbotInterface {
        +interactWithUser()
        +connectToControllers()
    }

    class UserLoginInterface {
        +authenticateUser(User)
    }

    class CourseSelectionInterface {
        +displayCourseOptions()
        +modifyCourses(User)
    }

    class CoursePlanInterface {
        +buildCoursePlan(User)
        +saveCoursePlan(User)
        +showGraduationGoal(User)
    }

    %% Connections between Control and Entities
    CourseController --> Course : interacts
    CoursePlanController --> CoursePlan : manages
    ChatController --> ChatHistory : handles
    UserController --> User : manages

    %% Relationships between boundary and control classes
    ChatbotInterface --> CourseController : "retrieves course data"
    ChatbotInterface --> CoursePlanController : "manages course plans"
    ChatbotInterface --> ChatController : "handles chat and downloads"
    UserLoginInterface --> UserController : "handles login and sessions"
    CourseSelectionInterface --> CourseController : "selects and filters courses"
    CoursePlanInterface --> CoursePlanController : "builds and saves course plan"
